ActCanada Shipping Act
PrecisEnactment of the WRECK DISTRICTS AND RECEIVERS OF WRECKS ORDER which (a) establishes 13 Wreck Districts covering all of Canada and appoints 19 employees of the Department of Transport as Receivers of Wrecks; and (b) repeals the previous Order made in 1997.
